These assholes harassed staff at the downtown soup kitchen demanding free food and assaulted people when they didn't get their way... let me repeat that so it sinks in: They harassed VOLUNTEERS for free food that's meant for the fucking homeless. Desecrated, and were drinking, dancing, partying on the National war memorial and the "tomb of the unknown soldier" (which is to honor/remember all those who never made it home from war). Also Desecrated the Terry Fox statue, as well as a number of other statues/monuments in the area (Being the capital, Ottawa has a number of statues, memorials, monuments, etc). They had to close most businesses due to harassment, threats, and assaults, as well as the main shopping mall downtown (Rideau Centre), as they were marching and chanting inside without masks and harassing retail workers. Oh, and rocks thrown at windows displaying pride flags. The list goes on of all the issues these fuckwits have caused, people who live & work in the downtown core of Ottawa are being held hostage, and are afraid to leave their residences. And now, someone has actually lost their life. They are walking in the street, holding up vehicles saying "I'm FREE to walk here"

